<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.7.3">
<l>puyaluṟu varaimaḻai poḻitara maṇinirai</l>
<l>mayaluṟa varaikuṭai yeṭuviya neṭiyavar</l>
<l>muyaltuḷar miḷaimuyal tuḷavaḷa viḷaivayal</l>
<l>kayaltuḷu kaṇapura maṭikaḷta miṭamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of god, the tall one who held up a mountain umbrella</l>
<l>When the lovely herd felt fear, as hail from a storm was made</l>
<l rend="indent">to stream down,</l>
<l>Is Kaṇṇapuram where the kayal fish leap in fertile, growing fields</l>
<l>While hares leap in the underbrush [away from] the work hoes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
